---
title: Spinach and Cheese-Topped Pork Chops with Oven Potatoes and Buttered Beans
description: Tonight we're trying something new! We are turning this pork chops into a luxury meal topped with a luscious cheesy spinach dip. Oven-roasted potatoes and buttered green beans make a meal the whole family can get behind!
